	<h2>
			What is MedicalPhoto ?		</h2>








<p> MedicalPhoto is a non-commercial medical image management program. MedicalPhoto have been developed for the dermatologist, but it also can be used for plastic surgeon and dentist.</p>
<p><br />This program was developed for the purpose of use in dermatology Asan Medical Center in 2007. Clinical picture was taken 200-300 daily, It was developed to easily and efficiently manage the photos. It was a series of repetitive tasks to organize clinical photos. As a large number of clinical photography that has accumulated over the years, it takes a lot of time to look for a photo in Windows. Pictures can be found within 1 second in MedicalPhoto, based on the database that is built in. MedicalPhoto has a ICD-10 diagnosis and an additional diagnosis of most of the Textbook of dermatology. It is also possible to define your diagnosis or procedure name if the diagnosis is not defined as a reserved word, and you can tag it to your photos. MedicalPhoto supports multiple monitors. If you have 2-3 monitors, you can compare the photos on multiple monitors. As MedicalPhoto has server-client structure, if there are a large number of computers in your office, you can access the picture from anywhere in the office.</p>
<p> </p>
